                  <span class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-[#CFE8B3] -mt-1" style="font-family: 'Noto Naskh Arabic', 'Traditional Arabic', 'Arabic Typesetting', serif;" dir="rtl">الحديقة</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[#CFE8B3] leading-relaxed text-base">We eliminate what <span class="italic font-semibold">bugs</span> you.</p>
